	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Alchemy</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP">
			<Text>Researchers using the intense radiation of a nuclear reactor have developed a cost effective way of transmuting elements, within reason. We could certainly make use of this technology.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Transmute 2 [ICON_RES_IRON] into a copy of the slightly heavier [ICON_RES_COPPER] Copper.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Transmute 4 [ICON_RES_IRON] into 8 copies of the lighter [ICON_RES_ALUMINUM] Aluminum.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Transmute 2 [ICON_RES_URANIUM] into 2 copies of the slightly lighter [ICON_RES_GOLD] Gold.</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Let's try something we need more of. Copper wire is extremely expensive these days, any chance we could make some more?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>In the near future I am going to need a large amount of Aluminum. Possible?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>So we can't do Iron to Gold? Disappointing. How about something else? Uranium?</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
